緊假少左車"},{"pid":"fcd01329107aaeb6464f500f75f525e72f15831e","tid":27843,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-13T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>考三點幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢條仆街路，咩野時段都多車架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個時好彩啲學校仲放緊假少左車</blockquote><br />\n你就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008c2bde3256a1771cf06c9d51db4f6d95c6d340","tid":27843,"uid":7291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-13T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"培正道 好耐之前一take pass<br />\n<br />\n睇番哩個post 見番自己 唔明當時驚乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家放鬆啲 記住每個步驟前 大呼吸一下先諗清楚<br />\n<br />\n咁就無有怕"},{"pid":"4054fdddd647fd472709ced52f84a8e48718762c","tid":27843,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T14:04:25.000Z","msg":"其實考之前叫師傅兜一兜你行哂三條線有唔清楚嘅地方即時問哂佢 睇清睇楚就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a841b5561e997873d0cb93b57338538e5d0e65d7","tid":27843,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:13:39.000Z","msg":"頭先考左公主線<br />\n<br />\n衰路試，兩大剔，超越物體同未有留意交通情況<br />\n<br />\n應該係行窩山果時，太多車係兩邊，我冇擰足頭<br />\n<br />\n我都唔肯定係咪衰呢個位<br />\n<br />\n師父話出閘，泊車，掉頭做得好完美，好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢仲話希望我第二次考抽到第二個試場，唔駛考呢條仆街路，咁就穩陣好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n七日後排快期又一條好漢<br />\n<br />\nBtw, 貨車狗私家車狗我屌晒你地老母，一路考公主道，貨車係後面貼得勁埋砵鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有架私家車唔打燈係忠孝街突然係右面cut鳩我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7b46d7d47a26d7c0d776c1187e8fab7fbbe086","tid":27843,"uid":18927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先考左公主線<br />\n<br />\n衰路試，兩大剔，超越物體同未有留意交通情況<br />\n<br />\n應該係行窩山果時，太多車係兩邊，我冇擰足頭<br />\n<br />\n我都唔肯定係咪衰呢個位<br />\n<br />\n師父話出閘，泊車，掉頭做得好完美，好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢仲話希望我第二次考抽到第二個試場，唔駛考呢條仆街路，咁就穩陣好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n七日後排快期又一條好漢<br />\n<br />\nBtw, 貨車狗私家車狗我屌晒你地老母，一路考公主道，貨車係後面貼得勁埋砵鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有架私家車唔打燈係忠孝街突然係右面cut鳩我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考幾點?我到星期一就岩岩好7個工作天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf4a2041cc8a57a82c71685db36dbab811e5a39","tid":27843,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:16:59.000Z","msg":"練得唔夠都係死因之一<br />\n<br />\n我學得22.5小時<br />\n<br />\n公主道條線練過兩次咁大把，我仲諗住唔係考1就3， 忽略左2線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd052745368df183259bdd640920a8ae4b7361e8","tid":27843,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:17:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頭先考左公主線<br />\n<br />\n衰路試，兩大剔，超越物體同未有留意交通情況<br />\n<br />\n應該係行窩山果時，太多車係兩邊，我冇擰足頭<br />\n<br />\n我都唔肯定係咪衰呢個位<br />\n<br />\n師父話出閘，泊車，掉頭做得好完美，好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢仲話希望我第二次考抽到第二個試場，唔駛考呢條仆街路，咁就穩陣好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n七日後排快期又一條好漢<br />\n<br />\nBtw, 貨車狗私家車狗我屌晒你地老母，一路考公主道，貨車係後面貼得勁埋砵鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有架私家車唔打燈係忠孝街突然係右面cut鳩我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考幾點?我到星期一就岩岩好7個工作天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我考11點9"},{"pid":"96f84dcafd474b209b1cc6dd70d14cfbb70b5c56","tid":27843,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:19:39.000Z","msg":"仆街考官一上黎個心跳得幾撚快<br />\n<br />\n泊車果時又行左落車睇，攪到我以為自己肥左"},{"pid":"d27f957c81ba5a04ca994a376dfb927159520517","tid":27843,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:59:47.000Z","msg":"低能野想問<br />\n<br />\n紅綠燈起步你地有無望盲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外暫時停車(燈位，讓線, 塞車)<br />\n拉手制後有無入埋N波，定照handbrake 同腳brake一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有公主道轉入忠民街前，係咪當過線？盲左盲點？<br />\n<br />\n有無睇埋右邊盲點？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔同師傅唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465091f4c783251c3a2530ce1998eef907514e5d","tid":27843,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:59:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>練得唔夠都係死因之一<br />\n<br />\n我學得22.5小時<br />\n<br />\n公主道條線練過兩次咁大把，我仲諗住唔係考1就3， 忽略左2線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公主道條線好少機會可以入 得夜晚學車先入得去<br />\n下次試下約夜晚學車"},{"pid":"49bc3cf6bc2d9e9f3213ec812994fbf8b8f144f3","tid":27843,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:05:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>低能野想問<br />\n<br />\n紅綠燈起步你地有無望盲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外暫時停車(燈位，讓線, 塞車)<br />\n拉手制後有無入埋N波，定照handbrake 同腳brake一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有公主道轉入忠民街前，係咪當過線？盲左盲點？<br />\n<br />\n有無睇埋右邊盲點？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔同師傅唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常應該唔會點望呀嘛 你都係行緊同一條線嚟 斷估唔會有人咁白痴燈位都未過就cut你線呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我燈位就入硬N 同時腳唔鬆hb就一定拉"},{"pid":"eea0a6b27121db54c6bbe7b37cf1756979644171","tid":27843,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆街考官一上黎個心跳得幾撚快<br />\n<br />\n泊車果時又行左落車睇，攪到我以為自己肥左</blockquote><br />\n我個官好好人<br />\n考3手軚嗰時緊張放左手制先入波都無肥我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泊位又就係咁2坐住睇兩睇就剔左pass"},{"pid":"5eb5e7cb5f95807dc1aeaa88dd9083d95d0f9646","tid":27843,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T03:32:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仆街考官一上黎個心跳得幾撚快<br />\n<br />\n泊車果時又行左落車睇，攪到我以為自己肥左</blockquote><br />\n我個官好好人<br />\n考3手軚嗰時緊張放左手制先入波都無肥我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泊位又就係咁2坐住睇兩睇就剔左pass</blockquote><br />\n你就好<br />\n<br />\n過兩星期排快期<br />\n<br />\n都唔知中邊個試場了<br />\n<br />\n話就話其他兩個試場易考過培正道<br />\n<br />\n不過，都需要上返唔知幾多堂適應"},{"pid":"88da86ea265dd3860a6c2b10d58ac9672a7e99fd","tid":27843,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:30:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仆街考官一上黎個心跳得幾撚快<br />\n<br />\n泊車果時又行左落車睇，攪到我以為自己肥左</blockquote><br />\n我個官好好人<br />\n考3手軚嗰時緊張放左手制先入波都無肥我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泊位又就係咁2坐住睇兩睇就剔左pass</blockquote><br />\n你就好<br />\n<br />\n過兩星期排快期<br />\n<br />\n都唔知中邊個試場了<br />\n<br />\n話就話其他兩個試場易考過培正道<br />\n<br />\n不過，都需要上返唔知幾多堂適應</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日考fail左？"},{"pid":"439322e00e1ea5ff818445ccf7dcfb2a330aab73","tid":27843,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T14:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我個官好好人<br />\n考3手軚嗰時緊張放左手制先入波都無肥我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泊位又就係咁2坐住睇兩睇就剔左pass</blockquote><br />\n你就好<br />\n<br />\n過兩星期排快期<br />\n<br />\n都唔知中邊個試場了<br />\n<br />\n話就話其他兩個試場易考過培正道<br />\n<br />\n不過，都需要上返唔知幾多堂適應</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日考fail左？</blockquote><br />\n咪星期五考肥左路試，乙部Pass<br />\n<br />\n衰超越物體同過線冇留意交通情況， 兩個大剔"},{"pid":"0242548fda8f59e5c6d7494f263d6aaccab2e8f2","tid":27843,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:31:51.000Z","msg":"好多死車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過死車個陣<br />\n<br />\n係咪同死車司機位平排個陣望一望佢？<br />\n<br />\n定係照過佢兩個車位先左鏡左盲點入線？"},{"pid":"4cbf39a55f34a8bf0af9d3153b25d3ec52734057","tid":27843,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:46:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多死車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過死車個陣<br />\n<br />\n係咪同死車司機位平排個陣望一望佢？<br />\n<br />\n定係照過佢兩個車位先左鏡左盲點入線？</blockquote><br />\n唔係架架都要望<br />\n依度好難解釋你聽幾時要望 問師傅啦<br />\n你考左啦咩"},{"pid":"473fae99d914e97920a48ff7a40f87e0c4e4a30c","tid":27843,"uid":60422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"上次考培正肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵快期容唔容易考番培正道?"},{"pid":"e25c4580f9ea4bbb364b8c4128fd440ee55f9ff1","tid":27843,"uid":74383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:51:40.000Z","msg":"我考個時停定 準備出試場 就有個廢老趕住死 咁就肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa9f2676acb65cef7483dffcb86e3c959b7337a","tid":27843,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529920a4165601600f7b4a9a49491868218fb547","tid":27843,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"Yoho<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a796d3be3e6a88cf4dca693a452e0a3f539fa2","tid":27843,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"今日走去排返丙部普通期<br />\n<br />\n又抽中返培正道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4月再戰，我唔會輸俾同一條賽道twice<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829986b4a6e89c2090508326281f08b4d5cf2daf","tid":27843,"uid":38167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"肥過兩次培正道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一次冇擰頭，一次比考官dup低<br />\n第三次抽到石蔭先pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 培正好難考"},{"pid":"22ab0ef93c56ea065e9ef80c96ccc8ff51898